artment where the frenzied pace of clinical care and heavy traffic volumes are the norm athenahealth is a networkenabled resultsoriented services company that offers medical record revenue cycle patient engagement care coordination and population health services for hospital and ambulatory clients the company’s vision is to build a national health information backbone to help make healthcare work as it should urgichart from edaris health delivers a valuable service for the increasingly important and rapidly growing medical specialty segment known as urgent care our saas clinical and electronic health record traces its heritage to an informatics solution developed for a hospitals emergency department where the frenzied pace of clinical care and heavy traffic volumes are the norm ken wolfe ceo edaris health as an mdp partner edaris health joins a network of likeminded healthcare professionals who are looking to disrupt established approaches in healthcare that simply aren’t working aren’t good enough or aren’t advancing the industry in addition to helping providers thrive in the face of industry change to learn more about edaris health’s new integrated application please visit edaris health’s product listing page in the athenahealth marketplace about edaris health edaris health provides easilydeployed saas  solutions for forwardthinking healthcare providers to meet the needs of today’s patients and providers the edaris health technology solution urgichart enables urgent care clinicians and healthcare providers to better serve patients who are seeking unscheduled and flexible access to care without compromising quality in care delivery the company’s products – urgichart flexchart and engagecare  are deployed at teaching and community hospitals and urgent care centers across the united states the clinical applications provided by edaris health are based on software technology developed over a tenyearperiod by emergency physicians and healthcare information technology specialists at beth israel deaconess medical center bidmc in boston a tertiary care hospital affiliate of harvard medical school  bidmc continues to serve as the company’s main research and development partner providing realworld clinical insights to constantly improve the edaris health suite of saas solutions  for more information please visit  wwwedarishealthcom    contact info ken wolfe ceo edaris health inc kwolfeedariscom  source edaris health share on facebook share on twitter categories healthcare healthcare technology hospitals and clinics healthcare and medical news tags athenahealth edaris health ehr healthcare technology urgent care urgent care ehr urgichart about edaris health view website the edaris health solutions includes urgichart  flexchart and engagecare that enable clinicians and other health care providers to better serve patients who are seeking unscheduled and flexible access to care without compromising quality company address edaris health  west stwaltham massachusetts  th floor waltham ma  united states more press releases forerun inc announces new corporate name change edaris health to reflect broader healthcare commitment edaris health  nov   newswire get notified about new releases sign up for email updates from newswire enter your email address notification frequency press releases instant daily never news instant daily never event instant daily never blog daily never facebook daily never twitter daily never subscribe forerun inc announces new corporate name change edaris health to reflect broader healthcare commitment  newswire forerun inc announces new corporate name change edaris health to reflect broader healthcare commitment press release  updated nov   waltham ma november   newswirecom  forerun inc a preeminent electronic clinical documentation display and decision support software and services company providing saasbased solutions to urgent care facilities and emergency departments announced today the changing of its corporate name to edaris health edaris this name change reflects the company’s broader offering of healthcare products and services following its recent merger with omedix inc the combination of these two organizations will allow edaris to significantly expand its market reach and achieve its goal of becoming a leader in delivering clinical it workflow and documentation solutions to the unscheduled care market additionally edaris now provides patient engagement and secured communication solutions that benefit both the patient and providers in targeted specialty ambulatory markets our new name – edaris health – recognizes our legacy solution in the emergency services arena as we expand our offering to primary care clinics with urgent care access services  edaris will provide next generation clinical informatics to meet the convenience of unscheduled visits while maintaining patient’s expectation for speed and quality of care said ken wolfe ceo of edaris health   the new name is effective immediately and will be implemented across the companys product and services throughout the calendar year  about edaris health the edaris health wwwedariscom solutions includes urgichart  flexchart and engagecare that enable clinicians and other health care providers to better serve patients who are seeking unscheduled and flexible access to care without compromising quality  edaris also supports the ehr and clinical workflow within urgicaremd a comprehensive urgent care application jointly designed and exclusively offered by henry schein medical systems  the company’s products are deployed at numerous teaching and community hospitals free standing eds ambulatory clinics and urgent care clinics across the us contact    destinee mack director of business development  edaris health i edariscom west street th floor east waltham ma i    dmackedariscom source edaris health share on facebook share on twitter categories healthcare healthcare and medical informatics healthcare technology tags edaris forer